'''表面冷凝器'''（surface condenser）是指安装在[[火力发电站|火力发电站]]的[[水冷|水冷]]{{link-en|壳管式换热器|Shell and tube heat exchanger}}，用于[[冷凝|冷凝]][[蒸汽轮机|蒸汽轮机]]排出的[[蒸汽|蒸汽]]<ref>{{Cite book|last={{link-en|Robert Thurston Kent}} (Editor in Chief)|title=Kents’ Mechanical Engineers’ Handbook|edition=Eleventh edition (Two volumes)|publisher=John Wiley & Sons (Wiley Engineering Handbook Series)|year=1936}}</ref><ref name="Babcock">{{Cite book|last=Babcock & Wilcox Co.|title=Steam: Its Generation and Use|edition=41st|year=2005|isbn=0-9634570-0-4}}</ref><ref name="Elliott">{{Cite book|last=Thomas C. Elliott, Kao Chen, Robert Swanekamp (coauthors)|title=Standard Handbook of Powerplant Engineering|edition=2nd|publisher=McGraw-Hill Professional|year=1997|isbn=0-07-019435-1}}</ref>。表面冷凝器是一种[[换热器|换热器]]，在低于[[大气压|大气压]]的压力下将蒸汽从[[气态|气态]]转化为[[液态|液态]]，同時這些液態水還能輸送至{{link-en|蒸汽发生器|Water-tube boiler}}或[[锅炉|锅炉]]中繼續使用。

